    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Uni-Charm Indonesia Tbk operates in the sanitary napkin industry in Indonesia. It operates through two segments: Diapers and Non Diapers. The company engages in the manufacture and sale of sanitary napkin, night wing, panty liners, and baby diapers; and feminine care, baby care, wellness care, and pet care. It also offers non-woven and tissue papers; and trading services. The company serves its products through CHARM, MamyPoko, Lifree, Fitti Pants, Certainty, Silcot, CharmNap Urine Dry, Unicharm pet, and Kirey Care Wipes brand names. PT Uni-Charm Indonesia Tbk was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Jakarta Selatan, Indonesia. PT Uni-Charm Indonesia Tbk is a subsidiary of Unicharm Corporation.",
